<view class="page">
  <!-- v3.0.5 阶段 3.9: 全局导航栏 -->
  <nav-bar title="5 元素速测" showHome="{{true}}" />


  <view class="header">
    <view class="title-main">5 元素速测</view>
    <view class="title-sub">公历生日 → 5 元素 (滋养对应, 不算命)</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="title-sub">您的公历生日</view>
    <picker mode="date" value="{{birthDate}}" bindchange="onPickDate" start="1940-01-01" end="2026-12-31">
      <view class="picker-view">公历生日 · {{birthDate || '轻触选择'}}</view>
    </picker>
    <view class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24rpx;" bindtap="onSubmit">看 5 元素</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{result}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">您的主元素</view>
      <view class="text-body" style="margin-top: 12rpx; color: #4a7c59; font-weight: 600; font-size: 36rpx;">
        {{result.wuxing}}
      </view>
      <view class="text-body" style="margin-top: 12rpx; color: #6b6b6b;">
        {{result.wuxingDesc}}
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">推荐经文 (3 篇)</view>
      <view class="text-body" wx:for="{{result.jingwen}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="j" style="margin-top: 12rpx;">
        • {{j.source}} · {{j.title}}
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">推荐汤品 (3 款)</view>
      <view class="text-body" wx:for="{{result.soups}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="s" style="margin-top: 12rpx;">
        • {{s.name}} — {{s.desc}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="compliance-bar">
    ✦ 5 元素是中医体质框架 (春木/夏火/长夏土/秋金/冬水), 不是命理。悦济不卖命理服务, 不收费。
  </view>
</view>
